<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Revolution_drum_corps_bass_drums.JPG" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d5/Revolution_drum_corps_bass_drums.JPG/250px-Revolution_drum_corps_bass_drums.JPG" width="250" height="188" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d5/Revolution_drum_corps_bass_drums.JPG/375px-Revolution_drum_corps_bass_drums.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d5/Revolution_drum_corps_bass_drums.JPG/500px-Revolution_drum_corps_bass_drums.JPG 2x" /></a>
